    "en": {
      "title": "The swearing in of the President is in a moment",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe, the 8th Executive President of Sri Lanka, is scheduled to take the oath of office today at 10.15 am.",
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe takes the oath of office in the presence of Chief Justice Jayantha Jayasuriya at the Sri Jayawardenepura Parliament Complex.",
        "Currently, the Parliament complex is being prepared in Lahilahi for the swearing-in ceremony."
      ],
